Wow, you can actually have a campfire in space.

190
00:21:52,732 --> 00:21:54,032
できるよ一応。
Well, technically you can.

191
00:21:54,132 --> 00:21:56,132
だって酸素があるってことだ！
That means there's oxygen!

192
00:21:56,232 --> 00:22:00,032
