We've arrived in space. Last year we were also
technically in space...

245
00:24:27,732 --> 00:24:31,032
あんまり見えないかもしれないですね。
...but you might not have been able to see it as well.

246
00:24:31,132 --> 00:24:35,832
だから今年はちゃんと宇宙に行きたいですって。
So this year, I really wanted us to go to
space properly.

247
00:24:36,832 --> 00:24:41,032
わ～すごい！宇宙来ました、二人で。
Wow, amazing! The two of us have come to space.

248
00:24:41,132 --> 00:24:42,532
すごい！
It's amazing!

249
00:24:43,032 --> 00:24:45,532
あ、綺麗本当に。
Ah, it's really beautiful.

250
00:24:45,732 --> 00:24:49,032
お、なんか姉さんと似合うじゃん？
Hey, doesn't it suit you, Sora-neesan?

251
00:24:49,132 --> 00:24:50,032
本当？
Really?

252
00:24:50,132 --> 00:24:53,032
そう、なんか普通にイメージカラーが青だから。
Yeah, since your image color is blue.

253
00:24:53,132 --> 00:24:54,532
ね。
Right.

254
00:24:54,632 --> 00:24:57,032
ほら、合うの、ステージもこっちも。うん。
